resBody.itemText: Photo #@taken# on \n Feb 24, 2017 #@shows# a partly melted ice sculpture at the Ice and Snow World in Harbin, capital of Northeast China's Heilongjiang province, Feb 24, 2017. Ice sculptures began to melt as temperature rose recently. [Photo/Xinhua]
